        {
          "name": "0. QUICK START - Read First!",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/api/messages",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["api", "messages"]
            },
            "description": "üöÄ QUICK START GUIDE:\n\n1. Go to Authentication ‚Üí Signup (Create User 2)\n2. Copy user._id from response ‚Üí Set as {{receiverId}}\n3. Go to Authentication ‚Üí Login (User 1)\n4. Copy token from response ‚Üí Set as {{authToken}}\n5. Copy user._id from response ‚Üí Set as {{userId}}\n6. Run: Start Conversation\n7. Copy conversationId ‚Üí Set as {{conversationId}}\n8. Run: Send Message ‚úÖ\n\n---\n\nAll working endpoints:\n‚úì Start Conversation\n‚úì Send Message (THIS IS WHAT YOU WANT!)\n‚úì Get Conversations\n‚úì Get Conversation Messages\n‚úì Mark Message as Read\n‚úì Delete Message\n‚úì FCM Token Registration\n‚úì FCM Notifications\n‚úì Topic Management\n‚úì Logout with FCM Cleanup\n"
          },
          "response": []
        },
